OS operating system đc chia thành 3 lớp : app,kernel,hardware and device driver
kernel translate request from one layer
Mobile os runnng on linuxkernel

Lolipop đc giới thiệu Android runtime ART
Android release 2008 , last lolipop version in No 20,2014

Dặc điểm Android:Ease of Programming, 2d3d graphic àn animation,multi language,Web browser, Multi touch, connectivity, Mediaprocessing, sensor support,Storage Capabilipity
                ,Large Market Share,Abstraction of hardware diferences, open source, free to use, ease to use,google now
				
Linux Kernel: base layer, communicate với hardware,responsible for connected device,interact với librabies layer
Librari:contain librabies,surface manager, openGL,media framework ,Webkid, freetype,ssl, sqlite
Android Runtime part of librabies,similar JVM, replace for Davilk
APP framework:manage app for basic functioning, consist:ActivityManager, Pakage manager,...interact with APP layer
APP layer : consist : application,default and install application,interact with other layer
SDK software development kit:a package consist all tool requied for development app
SDK come with:documentation, librabies,sample code,emulator,guides,Androidstudio IDE


AVD android virtual device is an android emulator, funtion similar to a mobile device
AVD consist:hardware features, software,look of the screen
APP component:Activity,service content provider, broadcast receiver,resource, asset , layout

Activity life cylcle:State:Active , Paused,Stopped, inactive
                     Method:oncreate,onstart,onresume,onpause,onstop,ondestroy,onrestart
					 lifrtime:full, visible, active
Service             :Service form:started, bound
                     method:context.startservice,onstartcommand,oncreate,context.stopservice,context.bindservice,onbind
Content provider :provice access data, crud
                  method :oncreate,query,insert	update , delete, gettype	
Broadcast receiver:receive and response anoucement
                  method:abortBroadcast,clearabortBroadcast	,getabortBroadcast,getdebugunregister ,getresultcode,getresultdata
Resource :static content, animation,drable...
Assets, similar resource ,file system
Layout:Linear,Relative,table,absolute,frame,listview, gridview
Intent: activate component
intent filter select intent that can manage
Share preferences:CheckbocPreference,listpreference,edittextreference, define in xml, preferences manager class use to save preferences

Notification:Small icon,Title, detaitext
            Type:Nomal, basic,expanded progress, headup,lockScreec
Basic concept of UI:View , layout, ui component
UI component:input control,input event,menus,actionbar,setting, dialog,addition view(Tab host, Web view,searchview),status notification,toast,search, drag and drop	

UIComponent biuld using view ỏ viewgroup,  view đực biết đến như widgets
concept of view : focus, listener,atribute:id,settign, padding,size ,view location		

Listener even:conlick,onlongclick,onforcuschange,onkey, ontouch,oncreatecontextmenu
Adapter là cầu nối giữa ui và source
Type of Adapter:BaseAdapter,SimpleAdapter,ArrayAdapter,SimpleCursorAdapter,CursorAdapter,ResourceCursorAdapter,SpinerAdapter,SimpleCursorTreeAdapter,CursorTreeAdapter,HeaderViewListAdapter,
WrapperLstAdapter


data Storage option:Share preferences,Internal, External,Sqlitedatabase

Share preferences user key/value to save and get
package quan trọng sqlite,sqliteopenhelper,sqlitedatabase,cursorsqlexception

method ò curcor:get coulum index,getcoulumnName,getcoulumnNames,getcolumnindexofthrow,getcount,getposition,movetoposition,motofirst,motonext,movetoprevious
                          					 